original: Hallerbäck, Ivar Emanuel, kyrkoherde, Moho’lm, f. 13/8/01 d Norra Björke, Älvsb. i. G. 29 m. Gurli Ing-vast. Barn: Per-Axe’l f. 30, Birgitta 34, Lena 39. — Stud :ex. i Upps. 23, teoi. fil. ex. i Lund 25, teol. kand. 27, prakt. teol. ex. i Upps. 28, prästv. i Skara ’S. à. Res. t. Estland. V. pastor i Börstig 28, kommin. i Berg 29, i Tidaholm 35, kyrkoh. i Hjälstad fr. 41. Ordf. i Hjälstad, Vad, Mo o. Svenneby kyrkoråd o. kyrkostämma, ordf. i skolstyr. samt insp. v. samreal-s kol an i T öreboda.
translated: Hallerbäck, Ivar Emanuel, clergyman, born August 13, 1901 in Moholm, died in Norra Björke, Älvsborg county. Married to Gurli Ing-vast in 1929. Children: Per-Axel, born in 1930, Birgitta born in 1934, Lena born in 1939. He studied in Uppsala and Lund, where he earned degrees in theology, and later completed practical theology studies in Uppsala in 1928. He was ordained in Skara in the same year and served as a pastor in Börstig then Berg, and later Tidaholm. He served as the church leader in Hjälstad from 1941. He was the chairman of the church council and church meeting in Hjälstad, Vad, Mo and Svenneby. He was also the chairman of the school board and the inspector of the Samrealskolan in Töreboda.
